  <!-- ── Part B: Herd Immunity Threshold formula ── -->
  <text x="18" y="284" font-family="Arial" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#000000">B. Herd Immunity Threshold: Hc = 1 − 1/R₀</text>

